column2: SELECT top # s.ra, s.dec, s.dered_g, s.dered_r, p.oiii_#_reqw as oir, p.h_beta_reqw as hbr, p.nii_#_reqw as nir, p.h_alpha_reqw as har, p.oiii_#_reqw_err as oir_e, p.h_beta_reqw_err as hbr_e, p.nii_#_reqw_err as nir_e, p.h_alpha_reqw_err as har_e, p.specObjID      FROM galSpecLine as p   JOIN PhotoObjAll as s ON p.specObjID = s.specObjID    WHERE p.oiii_#_reqw_err ># AND p.h_beta_reqw_err ># AND p.nii_#_reqw_err ># AND p.h_alpha_reqw_err ># AND p.oiii_#_reqw/p.oiii_#_reqw_err ># AND p.h_beta_reqw/p.h_beta_reqw_err ># AND p.nii_#_reqw/p.nii_#_reqw_err ># AND p.h_alpha_reqw/p.h_alpha_reqw_err >#
